<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.5">
<l>tantai pukuntilaṉ nāṉiṅki runtilēṉ tōḻimā rāru millai</l>
<l>canta malarkkuḻa lāḷtaṉi yēviḷai yāṭu miṭamku ṟuki</l>
<l>pantu paṟittut tukilpaṟṟik kīṟip paṭiṟaṉ paṭiṟu ceyyum</l>
<l>nantaṉ matalaikkiṅ keṉkaṭa vōmnaṅkā yeṉceykē ṉeṉcey kēṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Her father was not in, I was not there, [and] none of her friends were either.</l>
<l>What must we here do about Nanda’s son who, approaching the place</l>
<l rend="indent">where [my] girl with lovely flowers in her hair</l>
<l>Was playing alone, snatching her ball, grabbing and tearing her clothes,</l>
<l>Committed a villain’s villainy? Lady, what do I do? What do I do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
